#Concept

* For leased line connections
* enabled by default for serial connections
* HDLC: Cisco Proprietry
* PPP: Industry standard for point to point leased lines
    * supports featureslike authentication
    * CHAP (challenge handshake authentication protocol) and PAP
    * hostname = username

#Configuration

* show controllers serial 0/0: shows DTE/DCE, clock rate and type of cable connected

##PPP

    # encapsulation ppp

* Uses hostname as username
* On R1
    
    * username R2 password cisco
    
    if* ppp authentication chap
    
    * debug ppp authentication

* On R2:
    
    * username R1 password cisco

Password must match on both sides
    
